    "text": "1) Put the flour in a clay bowl.2) Sprinkle a little...\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026 and salt and start mixing the flour.3) Add water as you mix the flour.4) Move the hand in a circular movement.5) Continue this for a \u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026.. minutes.6) Afterwards, pour some water into another clay pot and tie a clean \u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026......covering the mouth.7) Put the pittu dough on top of the cloth. 8) Then cover the dough with another pot.9) Now put the pot on \u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026",
